response.overview: Lose weight and keep it off by combining the Weight Watchers Program and regular exercise.  Start with an easy-to-follow warm-up, *Followed by three 6-minute segments that combine calorie-burning aerobics with resistance moves that will tone both the upper and lower body, *End with a relaxed cool-down and stretching. This is the light intensity workout called Get Started
response.tagline: Weight Watchers - Get Started! - Light Intensity
response.title: Get In Shape: Get Started!
